   <head>SONNET [01] I.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">AH! then, how dear the Muse's favors cost,</l>
     <l n="2">If those paint sorrow best — who feel it most!</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2">
     <l n="3">The well sung woes shall soothe my pensive ghost;</l>
     <l n="4">He best can paint them, who shall feel them most.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
